name: SG Ezeepak Kit Bag
description:
SG Ezeepak Kit Bag (Assorted, Backpack)



A dedicated sportsperson always keeps his equipment safe from damage and deformation by storing stuff in a quality bag. This SG Ezeepak Kit Bag has been designed for those cricket enthusiasts who love to spend their free time playing the sport.

Heavy duty nylon material

Made of heavy duty nylon material, this bag is durable and highly resilient to common damages.

Contemporary design

With a contemporary design, this bag is not only convenient to carry around but also looks stylish.

Foam padded adjustable shoulder straps

With foam padded adjustable shoulder straps, this bag is easy to carry around.

External bat pocket

The external bat pocket is where you can keep your bat and access it without having to open the bag.

One mesh pocket

Your accessories and small titbits can be placed in the mesh pocket of this kit bag.

Additional clip for helmet

For your helmet, this bag has an additional clip, thus making it easy for you to separate your other equipment from the helmet.
